::Ursa Major::

*As she slowly regains consiousness, she looks around trying to get her 
bearings.  She regains her holding on her functions and stand on all fours.*

"I wonders who else is here."

*She sniffs the air and catches the faint scent of other bots near by*

"I sure hope they are friendly.  I'd hate to run in with anyone who isn't."

*She goes back to her pod and takes out a small pack with a few small 
energon cuges in it.  She grabs the pack in her teeth and ambles throught 
the forest following her nose*
